04.jpg","floor":"#10","id":"1265860","time":"2017-7-24 00:09","userId":"mizudiwood","userName":"mizudiwood💿","userSign":"(19年小结→bgm.tv/blog/294448)","message":"举个例子，幸福花园","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/22/52202.jpg","floor":"#11","id":"1265861","time":"2017-7-24 00:12","userId":"52202","userName":"十六夜咲夜","userSign":"(我们的存在)","message":"编辑一拍大腿","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/42/14268.jpg","floor":"#11-1","id":"1266254","time":"2017-7-25 19:04","userId":"calfn","userName":"触触✅个人认证","userSign":"","message":"小裙子以下，过膝袜以上，刮掉了腿毛的那一截大腿"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/22/52202.jpg","floor":"#11-2","id":"1266455","time":"2017-7-26 18:14","userId":"52202","userName":"十六夜咲夜","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">柳胜薰CALFN-触触小扑洗VIP</span> 说: 小裙子以下，过膝袜以上，刮掉了腿毛的那一截大腿</q></div>怎么这么懂，是不是拍过"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/42/14268.jpg","floor":"#11-3","id":"1266470","time":"2017-7-26 19:35","userId":"calfn","userName":"触触✅个人认证","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">十六夜咲夜</span> 说: 怎么这么懂，是不是拍过</q></div>拍过，有毛，扎手"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/22/58/225835.jpg","floor":"#12","id":"1265862","time":"2017-7-24 00:25","userId":"nagaho","userName":"Nagaho","userSign":"(見えたぞ、エンディングが)","message":"没有人说琴梨吗？还有日香<br>看，那边有只琴梨","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/48/274827.jpg","floor":"#12-1","id":"1265877","time":"2017-7-24 01:49","userId":"kanzoso","userName":"橘花 梨樹","userSign":"","message":"琴梨和日香好像是官译"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/22/58/225835.jpg","floor":"#12-2","id":"1265893","time":"2017-7-24 08:58","userId":"nagaho","userName":"Nagaho","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">橘 理樹</span> 说: 琴梨和日香好像是官译</q></div>对的"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/12/83/128390.jpg","floor":"#13","id":"1267231","time":"2017-7-28 05:10","userId":"128390","userName":"渐渐融化的飘雪","userSign":"","message":"没有正版代理的话看原文有无汉字，没有汉化组直接选用常见汉字名/音译，有时候作者很后面才给出汉字就很x疼……<br>比如我一开始看东京食尸鬼，按照音译女主叫雾岛多卡来着？反正跟董香差很多，我记得当时汉化组还出来说不知道女主这名字怎么翻就先音译作这个名字吧。然后弟弟翻作雾岛绫人，结果后面成了雾岛绚都_(:з」∠)_要给汉字早点给啊(╯‵□′)╯︵┻━┻","sub":[]}]